> **BACL (unified, all IEEE 754 binary formats, normal + subnormal).** Let `a, b ∈ 𝔽⁺` in any IEEE 754 binary format (float16, float32, float64; normal or subnormal). If `ulp(a) ≥ ulp(b)`, then
